com.facebook.buck.features.ocaml

Class OcamlPlatform.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.features.ocaml.OcamlPlatform.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    OcamlPlatform

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class OcamlPlatform.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type OcamlPlatform. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.

      • from

        public final OcamlPlatform.Builder from(OcamlPlatform instance)
        Fill a builder with attribute values from the provided OcamlPlatform instance. Regular attribute values will be replaced with those from the given instance. Absent optional values will not replace present values. Collection elements and entries will be added, not replaced.
        Parameters:
        instance - The instance from which to copy values
        Returns:
        this builder for use in a chained invocation
